remarks: Note: This species is published in: Heinrich, 1921: 827, dd. Mar. 1st, 1921. and later on Aug. 31st,, 1921, again by the same authors. The misspelling of the genus name occurred in the original publication

NOTE: Gielis (2003) synonymized potentellus with T. pygmaeus. However, Matthews (2006) found potentellus to be distinct from T. pygmaeus based on larval characters. It is formally returned to species status herein (rev. stat.)

NOTE: Gielis (1993, 2003) treated meyricki as a synonym of H. fieldi. Matthews (2006) found these to be distinct species based on morphology of the genitalia, larvae, and pupae, as well as the use of different larval hostplants. It is formally reinstated herein (rev. stat.).
